      <textAnnotation id="sid-B81CA5DA-0F69-4F54-8547-C120EB39ED63" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>if the status is “More info required”, then Tech/Buyer  will provide the update manually​</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-777C0152-0E8A-4E3D-B8CE-D718F06E828F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Intel must approve all warranty claim responses resulting in less than full warranty credit.​​
Supplier warranty claim responses for full credit will be automatically status with “Intel Approved”​​</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F068289E-CD64-4680-89DC-9EF49265B62A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Warranty validation engine​</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7533EAF5-BA0D-4C86-8FA6-D3C01A4757C6" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>This will be in a form of master warranty storing part warranty info. The start date will be based on GR into warehouse or Installation Date with pre-defined duration of each part​​</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-779AC238-7D40-4961-B209-FDC50D741976" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>This will be Based on QUAL/ SUSTAIN / EXTEND Warranty Start Date </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F4485F7A-FF11-430A-BCAB-6FC6C8F961BA" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Internal Intel Owned Supplier​</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-D906F240-DC11-4C85-8551-B0A08B6D2DA2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If Status is “More 
info required”, then 
Tech/Buyer will 
provide the update 
manually</text>
      </textAnnotation>
